"par_id7587206\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">When enabled, the current slide shows the objects of the master slide.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານ, ສະໄລ້ປັດຈຸບັນຈະສະແດງວັດຖຸຂອງສະໄລ້ຕົ້ນແບບ.</ahelp>"

#. z7z7h
#: 03080000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03080000.xhp\n"
"par_id3257545\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Opens a file dialog to select a picture. The picture will be scaled and inserted on the background of the current master slide.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບໄຟລ໌ເພື່ອເລືອກຮູບພາບ. ຮູບພາບຈະຖືກປັບຂະໜາດ ແລະ ແຊກລົງໃນພື້ນຫຼັງຂອງສະໄລ້ຕົ້ນແບບປັດຈຸບັນ.</ahelp>"

