#. MF87J
#: 03090000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03090000.xhp\n"
"par_id3152597\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SD_BTN_OUTLINE\">Switches to outline view, where you can add, edit and reorganize slide titles and headings.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_SD_BTN_OUTLINE\">ປ່ຽນເປັນມຸມມອງໂຄງຮ່າງ, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມ, ແກ້ໄຂ ແລະ ຈັດລະບຽບຫົວຂໍ້ສະໄລ້ ແລະ ຫົວຂໍ້ຍ່ອຍໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. 3eAds
