"help.text"
msgid "The <menuitem>Text Formatting</menuitem> bar contains the following icons for slide titles:"
msgstr "ແຖບ <menuitem>ການຈັດຮູບແບບຂໍ້ຄວາມ</menuitem> ປະກອບມີໄອຄອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສຳລັບຫົວຂໍ້ສະໄລ້:"

