msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຄລິກປຸ່ມໃດໜຶ່ງເພື່ອຍ້າຍເອັບເຟັກອານິເມຊັນທີ່ເລືອກຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງໃນລາຍການ.</ahelp>"

#. DRU5t
#: 06060000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06060000.xhp\n"
"par_idN107F0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Category"
msgstr "ໝວດໝູ່"

#. kGugf
#: 06060000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06060000.xhp\n"
"par_idN107EF\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Select an animation effect category.</ahelp> The following categories are available:"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເລືອກໝວດໝູ່ເອັບເຟັກອານິເມຊັນ.</ahelp> ມີໝວດໝູ່ດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. zwSGz
#: 06060000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06060000.xhp\n"
"par_idN10571\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Entrance:</emph> Select an entrance effect from the list of effects."
msgstr "<emph>ທາງເຂົ້າ:</emph> ເລືອກເອັບເຟັກທາງເຂົ້າຈາກລາຍການເອັບເຟັກ."

#. SPBRU
#: 06060000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06060000.xhp\n"
"par_idN10578\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Emphasis:</emph> Select an emphasis effect from the list of effects."
msgstr "<emph>ເນັ້ນ:</emph> ເລືອກເອັບເຟັກເນັ້ນຈາກລາຍການເອັບເຟັກ."

#. 6Sbzp
#: 06060000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06060000.xhp\n"
"par_idN1057F\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Exit:</emph> Select an exiting effect from the list of effects."
msgstr "<emph>ທາງອອກ:</emph> ເລືອກເອັບເຟັກທາງອອກຈາກລາຍການເອັບເຟັກ."

