msgctxt ""
"06060000.xhp\n"
"par_idN1080B\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Selects the additional properties of the animation. Click the <emph>Options</emph> button to open the <link href=\"text/simpress/01/effectoptions.xhp\">Effect Options</link> dialog, where you can select and apply properties.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເລືອກຄຸນສົມບັດເພີ່ມເຕີມຂອງອານິເມຊັນ. ຄລິກປຸ່ມ <emph>ຕົວເລືອກ</emph> ເພື່ອເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງ <link href=\"text/simpress/01/effectoptions.xhp\">ຕົວເລືອກເອັບເຟັກ</link>, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ ແລະ ນຳໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດຕ່າງໆໄດ້.</ahelp>"

